{
  "texts": [
    "Given the environmental state, the GDM-based model, enhanced by exploration during the denoising process, produces a contract design that delivers a utility value of 280.85 for the MLLM service provider, which is higher than the 233.2 achieved by DRL-PPO.",
    "This advantage arises from GDM's capability to generate nearoptimal contracts.",
    "Additionally, as the type of healthcare data holder increases, the rewards they receive also rise.",
    "However, DRL-PPO shows consistent variables for the type-1 healthcare data holders, indicating a tendency towards local optimal solutions, which may not align with global interests.",
    "Overall, this numerical analysis highlights the practical feasibility and superior performance of the proposed GDM-based scheme."
  ]
}